Antioch and the Templars

00:25:34.080 --> 00:25:36.110 align:middle line:90%
abandoned the enclave.

00:25:36.110 --> 00:25:39.195 align:middle line:84%
In the 1270s, the
Tripoli enclave crumbled.

00:25:39.195 --> 00:25:44.380 align:middle line:90%


00:25:44.380 --> 00:25:47.600 align:middle line:84%
Only the arrival of
Prince Edward of England,

00:25:47.600 --> 00:25:51.690 align:middle line:84%
the future Edward I, with
10,000 Mongol allies,

00:25:51.690 --> 00:25:56.350 align:middle line:84%
