00:26:08.980 --> 00:26:12.700 align:middle line:84%
160,000 infantry, and 100
Mangonel siege engines

00:26:12.700 --> 00:26:14.647 align:middle line:84%
around the Christian
capital of Acre.

00:26:14.647 --> 00:26:16.140 align:middle line:90%


00:26:16.140 --> 00:26:19.160 align:middle line:84%
