approved of such violence.

00:27:14.646 --> 00:27:19.800 align:middle line:90%


00:27:19.800 --> 00:27:23.930 align:middle line:84%
>>By the 13th century,
the crusading ideal

00:27:23.930 --> 00:27:28.120 align:middle line:84%
