00:27:51.150 --> 00:27:53.640 align:middle line:90%
the idea had become impractical.

00:27:53.640 --> 00:27:55.380 align:middle line:90%


00:27:55.380 --> 00:27:58.270 align:middle line:84%
So I think it would
be quite fair to say

00:27:58.270 --> 00:28:01.640 align:middle line:84%
that the Templars and the
other crusading orders

00:28:01.640 --> 00:28:03.745 align:middle line:90%
were left high and dry.

00:28:03.745 --> 00:28:08.020 align:middle line:90%


00:28:08.020 --> 00:28:10.600 align:middle line:84%
>>The Knights Templar
were now more vulnerable

00:28:10.600 --> 00:28:13.030 align:middle line:84%
than they could
possibly imagine.

00:28:13.030 --> 00:28:16.160 align:middle line:84%
Their entire reason for being
was the defense Holy Land,

00:28:16.160 --> 00:28:18.000 align:middle line:90%
and they had failed.

00:28:18.000 --> 00:28:21.025 align:middle line:90%


