against the Muslims,

00:28:38.170 --> 00:28:40.830 align:middle line:84%
storm clouds were
gathering back in Europe.

00:28:40.830 --> 00:28:42.790 align:middle line:90%


00:28:42.790 --> 00:28:44.520 align:middle line:84%
The Order of the
Temple of Solomon

00:28:44.520 --> 00:28:46.760 align:middle line:84%
was about to find itself
caught in the middle

00:28:46.760 --> 00:28:48.875 align:middle line:84%
of a cataclysmic
power struggle that

00:28:48.875 --> 00:28:53.240 align:middle line:84%
would shake Western
Europe to the very core.

